Taiyou Asano is a super shy high school student and the only person he can talk to is his childhood friend, Mutsumi Yozakura. It turns out that Mutsumi is the daughter of the ultimate spy family! Even worse, Mutsumi is being harassed by her overprotective, nightmare of a brother, Kyouichirou. What drastic steps will Taiyou have to take to save Mutsumi?! A spy family comedy - the mission begins!
(Source: MANGA Plus)
Action, Adventure, Drama, Fantasy, Horror, Psychological, Thriller

The second season of Yakusoku no Neverland. Fifteen children escape Grace Field House, a false paradise, hoping for a chance at freedom. Instead, they encounter plants and animals they have never before seen, and are chased by demons. The outside world is so beautiful, and yet is almost too cruel to face. Even so, the children refuse to give up. They are guided in their search for better lives only by a message from Minerva and a pen Norman left behind in order to fulfill their promise to return to the House to save those of their family who are still trapped within.
(Source: Aniplex of America) Note: Episode 1 streamed early on Amazon Prime on Jan 7, 2021. The regular TV broadcast started on Jan 8, 2021.

Raon was once a loyal assassin for House Robert until Derus killed him. Not willing to give up, Raon prayed for vengeance and woke as a member of House Sieghart, the most powerful noble house. Hell need all of their near-infinite resources to get revenge. Though he carried over knowledge of a powerful Flame Link technique, he also carries the Curse of Bitter Frost, something thats slowly killing him. As if that werent enough, the demonic embodiment of Wrath is trying to take over his body. (Source: Tapas)

After two decades of battling extradimensional monsters and protecting the world, Dae-in Lim is finally ready to retire and enjoy a peaceful life. However, the morning after his retirement party, he wakes up to find himself back in time before he even gained his powers. Armed with knowledge of the future, Dae-in is determined to secure his fortune and retire again, but this time within three years.
(Source: WEBTOONS, translated)
